path_node by A.Albore 2014

to compile:
catkin_make --pkg path_follower

to use (no install): 
cp  /home/aalbore/catkin_ws/devel/lib/path_follower/path_node  /home/aalbore/catkin_ws/src/path_follower/

examples of usage:
rosrun path_follower plan_node -s 4-classes-factorgraph.fg
rosrun path_follower path_node -w <waypoints file>


to install (and then use)
catkin_make install --pkg path_follower

NB: The waypoints are comma separated, from the 1st to the last.
e.g. -1,0.002,3.21,

